{
  "stem": "14060.9",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 378.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we gave them food and sometime clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, we helped them sort of to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, this went on till 1948.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly, one night, the Hungarian guards, or Russians, I'm not sure, shot at one of these trucks because they didn't stop at the border crossing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They killed one person, and then it became known that this escape route is going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And suddenly, a few days before Tisha B'Av, my uncle was arrested.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had good connection with the police.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Plenty paid for.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After two, three days, he was released.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then there was no more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in 19-- this was in 1948.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But in 1947, we-- we often had a lot of Jewish Russian soldiers coming into the business.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And sometime they-- we invited them to the house and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they used to exchange views.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They spoke Yiddish, we spoke German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know-- we could understand each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I'll never forget, there was a Russian captain, about a 45-year-old man in 1947, who came up to-- into our house.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "First we met him in the shop, and then we invited him for a meal and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he said to us, in Yiddish like that, [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The [YIDDISH] means 'the Russian thief' has got us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I've got a mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I've got a father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But you people should know to get away while you can.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We didn't know what he was talking about.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was a coalition government in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The Communists held some important portfolios, but it was normal life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "By the summer of 1948, just at the time when my uncle was arrested, things have changed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The Communists fused with Socialists under obvious pressure.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
